**Program Components**
| Component | Social Model | Medical Model |
|-----------|--------------|---------------|
| Activities | Yes | Yes |
| Meals | Yes | Yes |
| Personal care | Basic | Comprehensive |
| Nursing | Limited/none | RN on staff |
| Therapy | None | PT, OT, ST available |
